  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Standing still in the woods is a lonely cabin inhabited by one man. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through his story over a week as he slowly goes insane.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find meaning in this mystery?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/25204d4c6ab46e4ed0b2b0e8c0729102.poster.avif?t=1744664817\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/25204d4c6ab46e4ed0b2b0e8c0729102.webm?t=1744664817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/25204d4c6ab46e4ed0b2b0e8c0729102.mp4?t=1744664817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Game Loop:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find logs and light your fire. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your can opener and munch on some beans. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get scared!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sleep in your cozy bed.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/a244c38bbc199fe02f7e41741c1313c2.poster.avif?t=1744664817\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/a244c38bbc199fe02f7e41741c1313c2.webm?t=1744664817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/a244c38bbc199fe02f7e41741c1313c2.mp4?t=1744664817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Packed with jump scares. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized graphics to help immerse you in his story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings to unlock.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many different unique events per day.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many Easter eggs to find.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have fun and enjoy!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Standing still in the woods is a lonely cabin inhabited by one man. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through his story over a week as he slowly goes insane.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find meaning in this mystery?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/25204d4c6ab46e4ed0b2b0e8c0729102.poster.avif?t=1744664817\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/25204d4c6ab46e4ed0b2b0e8c0729102.webm?t=1744664817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/25204d4c6ab46e4ed0b2b0e8c0729102.mp4?t=1744664817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Game Loop:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find logs and light your fire. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your can opener and munch on some beans. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get scared!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sleep in your cozy bed.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/a244c38bbc199fe02f7e41741c1313c2.poster.avif?t=1744664817\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/a244c38bbc199fe02f7e41741c1313c2.webm?t=1744664817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566280/extras/a244c38bbc199fe02f7e41741c1313c2.mp4?t=1744664817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Packed with jump scares. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized graphics to help immerse you in his story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings to unlock.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many different unique events per day.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many Easter eggs to find.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have fun and enjoy!</strong></p>",
